snippet.title: Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Dolph Lundgren Interviews - Aquaman World Premiere Red Carpet
snippet.description:
Jason Momoa, Amber Heard (who yes, did wear a swim hat to the premiere), Dolph Lundgren, Patrick Wilson, Director James Wan and composer Rupert Gregon-Williams are interviewed on the red carpet for their movie Aquaman.

Plot: Arthur Curry learns that he is the heir to the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, and must step forward to lead his people and be a hero to the world.
